  "body": "Discussion: https://www.notion.so/New-Activity-View-34b9d4af750e468a91858a86675ace81\r\nDesign: https://www.figma.com/file/FkFClTCYKf83RJWoifWgoX/Wallet-v2?node-id=11019-134543\r\nArchitecture:\r\n\r\n![WalletActivityPart](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/491074/230379511-1ac3f36c-6e3e-4ebb-a565-3ef589e800be.jpeg)\r\n\r\n## Related Issues:\r\n- [x] [Wallet: Activity tab not loading 20 items at a time#9814](https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/issues/9814)\r\n- [x] [Refresh Transactions CurrencyAmount instances when format changes](https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/issues/9548)\r\n- [x] [Wallet: transaction hash must be present in activity (transaction details)#9022](https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/issues/9022)\r\n- [x] [Loading more transactions in Activity View resets the Listview #9617](https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/issues/9617)\r\n- [x] [Dummy loading items are clickable](https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/issues/10083)\r\n- [x] [Delay after clicking the Activity tab before the skeleton loading starts](https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/issues/10232)\r\n- [x] [Ensure transaction items are loaded sequentially on Activities list view](https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/issues/10233)\r\n- [ ] [Query contact public key using wallet address](https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/issues/10760)\r\n- [x] #11333\r\n- [x] #11377 \r\n- [x] #11412\r\n- [x] #11447\r\n- [x] https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/issues/11717\r\n- [x] https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/issues/11754\r\n- [x] Finalized status is never used\r\n\r\n## QML Components\r\n- [x] Account List with combined view\r\n- [x] New Header https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/issues/10330\r\n- [x] New Network selector https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/issues/10330\r\n- [x] #10333\r\n- [x] #10443\r\n- [x] #10432\r\n- [x] #10473\r\n- [x] #10542\r\n- [x] #10639\r\n- [x] #10583\r\n- [x] #10619\r\n- [x] #10751\r\n- [x] #10786\r\n- [x] #10787\r\n- [x] #10792\r\n- [ ] Activity Details Bridge Link\r\n- [x] #10776\r\n- [x] #10822\r\n- [x] #10823\r\n- [x] #10796\r\n \r\n## New features For activity\r\n- [x] #10366\r\n- [x] #11017\r\n- [x] #10251\r\n- [x] #10790\r\n- [ ] #10791\r\n- [x] #10762\r\n- [x] #10848\r\n- [x] Copy tx\r\n- [x] #12122\r\n- [x] #12123\r\n- [ ] #12093 - (Contract Deployment and Minting activity filtering\r\n- [x] #10246\r\n- [x] #10474\r\n- [x] #11139\r\n- [x] #11080\r\n- [ ] #12120\r\n\r\n## Combine View\r\n- [x] #10247\r\n\r\n## Extra\r\n- [x] #11233\r\n- [ ] #11171 - content-dependent filtering criteria: NFTs, Tokens (we show the list from assets)\r\n- [x] #9047\r\n- [x] Unknown token details view; details https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/issues/11043\r\n- [ ] Known counterparty (CEX) address detection https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/issues/10956\r\n- [x] #11566\r\n- [ ] Filter and show destroy event (community-related)\r\n- [ ] #11414\r\n- [x] https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/issues/11534\r\n- [x] #11564\r\n\r\n## Optimizations\r\n\r\n- [x] #11631\r\n- [x] #11173\r\n  - [x] #11597\r\n  - [x] #11598\r\n- [x] #11351\r\n- [x] #11018\r\n- [x] #11036\r\n- [x] #12077\r\n- [ ] Extend recipients model with name and ens\r\n\r\n## Cleanup\r\n- [x] #11380",
